A Handbook on Drug and Alcohol Abuse: The Biomedical Aspects nke Gail Winger, Frederick G
Woods bipụtara na New York site Oxford University Press na 1992
Mbipụta nke anọ, emelitere ya na isiakwụkwọ maka "Club Drugs"  , e bipụtara na 2004..
Akwụkwọ ahụ nwetara nnabata dị iche iche site na akwụkwọ akụkọ ahụike
Frederick Hofmann na Adele Hofmann bipụtara mbipụta mbụ na 1975 dị ka Handbook on Drug and Alcohol Abuse.
